\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1680:\"<p>Back in September the eshop / cart was upgraded to bring you easier access to your past purchases and free updates via your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;. Since September the old and new eshop/carts were running so access could still could be provided to everyone who had purchased items before September.</p><p>If you purchased items before September, over the past two days, your account has been migrated to the new eshop/cart. This migration triggered an email invoice for your past purchases which provides the details of your order, the download links and a link to your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;. <strong>There are <em>no</em> additional charges or fees associated with your account migration</strong>. The old eshop/cart has been discontinued and removed. The download link and code you received with your original order will no longer function as of today. Please access your purchases from your &#8221;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;.</p><p>I thank you in advance for your understanding and patience. Happy New Years to you and yours!</p><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/12/27/eshop-cart-upgrade/\">Eshop / Cart Upgrade</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com\">Connections</a>.</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~4/I-RYKsc1TFI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"http://connections-pr